    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example delivers a linear power band and a 7,900 RPM redline, paired with a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains composed thanks to a factory-spec limited-slip differential and reinforced rear subframe mounting points. Recent service includes a valve clearance adjustment and cooling system overhaul, ensuring the high-pressure VANOS system and rod bearings are within operating tolerances. This is a mechanically sorted enthusiast machine ready for the twisties.",
