      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain remains robust with a factory limited-slip differential ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains composed, with the rear subframe reinforced to address known platform fatigue. The high-revving valvetrain has been recently serviced, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and shim-and-bucket valve adjustment to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. Suspension kinematics are sharp, utilizing M-spec bushings and dampers for precise turn-in. A mechanically sound, high-performance machine optimized for the purist.",
